Class Summary 
Class Description
Controller
Detects input from button press which either starts or stops movement animation.
Main
Program that shows a moving duck.
Model
Simulation Model for moving duck, tied to viewer to render changes and controller to start and stop sim.
Viewer
Gui which is used to render moving duck animation.
